        {
            "title": "人行：下調各類結構性貨幣政策工具利率0.25厘",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">人民銀行副行長鄒瀾表示，人行將推出兩方面政策措施，下調各類結構性貨幣政策工具利率0.25厘，各類再貸款1年期利率降至1.25厘，其他期限利率同步調整。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鄒瀾表示，人行將完善結構性工具，並加大支持力度，進一步助力經濟結構轉型優化。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584920-%e4%ba%ba%e8%a1%8c%ef%bc%9a%e4%b8%8b%e8%aa%bf%e5%90%84%e9%a1%9e%e7%b5%90%e6%a7%8b%e6%80%a7%e8%b2%a8%e5%b9%a3%e6%94%bf%e7%ad%96%e5%b7%a5%e5%85%b7%e5%88%a9%e7%8e%870-25%e5%8e%98",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240415_FI_source-ap_ChinaEco-7.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 15:20:35",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "午後改善 滬指收跌13點 深指轉升0.41% 鋰業股反彈",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">內地A股午後稍微改善，滬市跌幅收窄，深市更倒升收市，兩市交投則回落至不足3萬億元(人民幣‧下同)。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250408_FI_source-ap_China-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">上證綜指今早低開19點後曾迅速反彈倒升，但在升6點、見4133點便乏力再上，未幾重新轉跌，早市尾段曾失守4100點，最低報4097點，跌28點點，午市雖然全程報跌，但未再跌穿早市低位；滬指最後收報4112點，跌13點或0.33%，成交 1.176萬億元。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">深證成指則於早市初段見全日低位，最低14155點，跌93點，未幾反彈倒升，最高報14328點，升80點，其後反覆回吐又再報跌，午後才有較明顯起色，成功轉升收市；深指收報14306點，升58點或0.41%，成交1.73萬億元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">滬深300指數也升9點或0.2%，以4751點收市；創業板指數升18點或0.56%，報3367點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20250407_FI_source-ap_China_Trump_Tariffs_25097181957222-2.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">各主要板塊其實跌多於升，重磅銀行股偏軟，農業銀行(01288)A股(601288.SH)跌2.01%，報7.33元；中國銀行(03988)A股(601988.SH)則跌0.73%，報5.43元；建設銀行(00939)A股(601939.SH)跌0.44%，報9.03元；工商銀行(01398)A股(601398.SH)微跌0.13%，報7.68元。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">鋰業股反彈，贛鋒鋰業(01772)A股(002460.SZ)漲4.26%，報72元；天齊鋰業(09696)A股(002466.SZ)升2.51%，報61.32元。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15584879-%e5%8d%88%e5%be%8c%e6%94%b9%e5%96%84-%e6%bb%ac%e6%8c%87%e6%94%b6%e8%b7%8c13%e9%bb%9e-%e6%b7%b1%e6%8c%87%e8%bd%89%e5%8d%870-41-%e9%8b%b0%e6%a5%ad%e8%82%a1%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20240307_FI_source-ap_AShare-8.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-01-15 15:15:44",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
